I chose flask.
follow the below to run the on the terminal of your choice

Run the Flask app: python app.py.


Access the endpoints:
GET /api/server-info to get the server's average load and available disk space.
GET /api/return-value to get the current return_value.
POST /api/return-value with a JSON payload {"return_value": "new_value"} to update the return_value.